    <item>
      <title>朝鲜向韩国发射可能携带垃圾的气球</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-18/urgent-north-korea-launches-balloons-likely-carrying-trash-toward-south-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社） — 韩国军方称，朝鲜周四恢复向韩国放飞可能载有垃圾的气球。几天前，朝鲜誓言要对所谓的韩国平民跨境散发传单活动作出回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-07-18/urgent-north-korea-launches-balloons-likely-carrying-trash-toward-south-korea</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 09:01:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚希望获得银行外汇暴利的一半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/nigeria-mulls-one-time-50-windfall-tax-on-bank-forex-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布计划对银行在去年奈拉贬值后获得的巨额货币收益所获得的暴利征收 50% 的一次性税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/nigeria-mulls-one-time-50-windfall-tax-on-bank-forex-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的重要经济会议表明党准备应对经济放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平誓言要让“高质量发展”成为世界第二大经济体的指导力量，但这并没有什么初步迹象表明，最高领导层正准备采取重大措施刺激需求或遏制房地产市场低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/china-vows-to-push-for-high-quality-development-as-top-mission</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 08:35:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟委员会主席冯德莱恩争取连任 争取绿党支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/eu-s-von-der-leyen-keeps-climate-goals-ahead-of-parliament-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩 (Ursula von der Leyen) 承诺维持欧盟的气候目标、增强竞争力和加强国防工业，她希望能够锁定欧盟执行机构主席的第二任期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/eu-s-von-der-leyen-keeps-climate-goals-ahead-of-parliament-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:46:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业配额抗议活动蔓延 孟加拉国面临停摆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在示威活动演变为暴力事件后，学生抗议者向总理谢赫·哈西娜施压，要求废除政府的就业配额制度，孟加拉国将从周四开始关闭交通网络和企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
